title: Hi all!
body:
Hi everybody!
I just transferred my account to Oce server from EUW.

My english is far from perfect but I'm improving :)

replies.body: I was bronze 4 last season and now im gold (preseason gold 4). Still proud of dat 2014 bronze icon doe {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
